Simple,Legal,is,a,legal,billing,and,payment,service,In,addition,to,sending,legal,bills,and,receiving,payments,Simple,Legal,also,scans,bills,for,potential,duplicate,charges,and,fraudulent,charges,and,alerts,the,customer,The,Simple,Legal,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Simple,Legal,with,other,applications,Public,documentation,is,not,available,API,access,comes,with,account,service